2011 BWF World Junior Championships
Tournament details
Edition 13th
Level International
Location Taoyuan City and Taipei

The 2011 BWF World Junior Championships were held in Taoyuan City and Taipei, Chinese Taipei from October 28 to November 6, 2011.
